<messaging:emailTemplate subject="CRM Rejected: Direct Sales {!RelatedTo.ASI_CRM_Sold_To__r.Name} {!RelatedTo.name} {!RelatedTo.owner.name}" recipientType="User" relatedToType="ASI_CRM_JP_Sales_Order__c"><messaging:htmlEmailBody ><html>    <body>    <STYLE type="text/css">        TH {font-size: 11px; font-face: arial;background: #CCCCCC; border-width: 1;  text-align: center }         TD  {font-size: 11px; font-face: verdana }         TABLE {border: solid #CCCCCC; border-width: 1}        TR {border: solid #CCCCCC; border-width: 1}     </STYLE>    <font face="arial" size="2">        <p>以下のダイレクトセールス申請が却下になりましたので至急ご確認ください。</p>        <p>Please note the following Direct Sales is rejected.</p>        <p>Rejected by 却下者: {!RelatedTo.LastModifiedBy.Name}</p>        <c:ASI_CRM_JP_ApprovalRejectionCom headerId="{!RelatedTo.Id}" />    </font>     <font face="arial" size="2">        <p>Owner 所有者: {!RelatedTo.owner.name}</p>        <p>Sales Order Number 受注番号: {!RelatedTo.name}</p>        <p>Ship To 納品先: {!RelatedTo.ASI_CRM_Ship_To__r.Name}</p>        <p>Sold To 売上先: {!RelatedTo.ASI_CRM_Sold_To__r.Name}</p>        <p>Bill To 請求先: {!RelatedTo.ASI_CRM_JP_Bill_To__r.Name}</p>        <p>Order Date 発注日: <apex:outputText value="{0, date, yyyy/MM/dd}"><apex:param value="{!relatedTo.ASI_CRM_Order_Date__c}" /></apex:outputText></p>        <p>Requested Date 納品日: <apex:outputText value="{0, date, yyyy/MM/dd}"><apex:param value="{!relatedTo.ASI_CRM_Requested_Date__c}" /></apex:outputText></p>        <p>Invoice Date 請求日: <apex:outputText value="{0, date, yyyy/MM/dd}"><apex:param value="{!relatedTo.ASI_CRM_Invoice_Date__c}" /></apex:outputText></p>        <p>Payment Option 支払い方法: {!RelatedTo.ASI_CRM_Payment_Option__c}</p>        <p>Payment Due Date 支払期日: <apex:outputText value="{0, date, yyyy/MM/dd}"><apex:param value="{!relatedTo.ASI_CRM_Payment_Request_Date__c}" /></apex:outputText></p>        <p>Customer PO No. お客様発注番号: {!RelatedTo.ASI_CRM_Customer_PO_No__c}</p>        <p>Total Amount 合計金額:                 <apex:outputText value="{0, Number, ###,###,###,##0}">                    <apex:param value="{!RelatedTo.ASI_CRM_Total_Amount__c}" />                </apex:outputText>        </p>        <p>JDE Remark 送り状備考: {!RelatedTo.ASI_CRM_Remark__c}</p>        <p>Remark 備考: {!RelatedTo.ASI_CRM_JP_Remark_2__c}</p>    </font>    <font face="arial" size="3">                <table border="1" >            <tr >                <th>SKU</th>               <th>Quantity 数量</th>               <th>UOM 単位</th>               <th>Applied Unit Price 申請単価</th>               <th>Total Price 合計金額</th>               <th> Approved Unit Price 承認済単価</th>               <th>EX PRJ Price 仕切価格</th>               <th>Lower than Approved Price 承認単価より低い</th>               <th>Remark 備考</th>            </tr>            <apex:repeat var="item" value="{!relatedTo.Sales_Order_Items__r}">                <tr>                    <td>{!item.ASI_CRM_SKU__r.Name}</td>                    <td>                        <apex:outputText value="{0, Number, ###,###,###,##0}">                            <apex:param value="{!item.ASI_CRM_Quantity__c}" />                        </apex:outputText>                    </td>                    <td>{!item.ASI_CRM_UOM__c}</td>                    <td>                        <apex:outputText value="{0, Number, ###,###,###,##0}">                            <apex:param value="{!item.ASI_CRM_Unit_Price__c}" />                        </apex:outputText>                    </td>                    <td>                        <apex:outputText value="{0, Number, ###,###,###,##0}">                            <apex:param value="{!item.ASI_CRM_Extended_Price__c}" />                        </apex:outputText>                    </td>                    <td>                        <apex:outputText value="{0, Number, ###,###,###,##0}">                            <apex:param value="{!item.ASI_CRM_JP_Base_Price__c}" />                        </apex:outputText>                    </td>                    <td>                        <apex:outputText value="{0, Number, ###,###,###,##0}">                            <apex:param value="{!item.ASI_CRM_SKU__r.ASI_CRM_Ex_Price__c}" />                        </apex:outputText>                    </td>                    <td>{!item.ASI_CRM_JP_Lower_than_Base_Price__c}</td>                    <td>{!item.ASI_CRM_JP_Remark__c}</td>                </tr>            </apex:repeat>                         </table>    </font>    <br/>    <font face="arial" size="2">        <p>内容を確認するには下のリンクをクリックしてください &nbsp;        <apex:outputLink value="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140, FIND('.com/',$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+3)}/{!RelatedTo.id}">こちら</apex:outputLink>            </p>        <p>To approve/reject this application, click this &nbsp;        <apex:outputLink value="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140, FIND('.com/',$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+3)}/{!RelatedTo.id}">link</apex:outputLink>            </p>    </font>    </body> </html></messaging:htmlEmailBody></messaging:emailTemplate>